    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/859e20c9bd267eceb155fdde77647973.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/7ad2d4c2085b19319264191a706727d7.poster.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/7ad2d4c2085b19319264191a706727d7.webm?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/7ad2d4c2085b19319264191a706727d7.mp4?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>操作机枪钻打碎深地岩土，突破一切阻碍，挖掘地下，发现宝贵的矿石，击败邪恶的对手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/f7d424fb5831d13dbaf98de82c22862f.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/500de8f6ff40736ce00096be8c9d4a60.poster.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/500de8f6ff40736ce00096be8c9d4a60.webm?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/500de8f6ff40736ce00096be8c9d4a60.mp4?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>发掘深藏地底的古代文物，汇聚稀罕宝石与矿产。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/6c3479c68c912254116c982fb5c8bd41.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/5485aba3f70ec035f5aa3ba07108beb3.poster.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/5485aba3f70ec035f5aa3ba07108beb3.webm?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/5485aba3f70ec035f5aa3ba07108beb3.mp4?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>获得强大的升级项目，解锁新的能力，将你普通的自旋翼机变成不可小觑的武器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/0e82a8135f66aa7eb9334260de5fe971.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/75f5850e730194225ce7e7f5eaf21bff.poster.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/75f5850e730194225ce7e7f5eaf21bff.webm?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/75f5850e730194225ce7e7f5eaf21bff.mp4?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索多种自然环境——这里既有艰险的火山洞窟，也有郁郁葱葱的地下树林，每种环境都有各自特殊的挑战和奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/18881dad5ccb3cab82237f98e0896130.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 快节奏破土，采掘场面刺激<br></li><li>  即便流程失败，也不会受到惩罚，可以不断成长<br> </li><li> 多种自然环境等你探索<br> </li><li> 购买升级项目，武装你的自旋翼机<br> </li><li> 穿越游戏的主世界，解锁新的矿道<br> </li><li> 获得稀罕宝石、矿石和文物，令装备和能力升级<br> </li><li> 关卡是程序生成，适合无限重玩</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/ae1710d635cc4d955f004bbf0ff6f8ee.poster.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/ae1710d635cc4d955f004bbf0ff6f8ee.webm?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/ae1710d635cc4d955f004bbf0ff6f8ee.mp4?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《深地爆破采掘》借鉴了《Motherload》和《Galactic Mining Corp》等采矿游戏，加入了动力十足的场景，加快了游戏节奏。玩家如果喜欢挖掘、收集，那么应该会很喜欢这款作品。与此同时，游戏还有很多危险的敌人和神秘的物品，就算是经验丰富的矿工也不能掉以轻心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/998b60ef12bce672d6952cf513825e77.poster.avif?t=1739656976\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/998b60ef12bce672d6952cf513825e77.webm?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398170/extras/998b60ef12bce672d6952cf513825e77.mp4?t=1739656976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
